{"title":"为土豆歌唱","authors":["阿古拉泰"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":11,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为土豆歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿古拉泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩埋进黄土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并非死亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一生的开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奉献果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深入土壤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生一世都被埋没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生一世　悄悄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积攒着热量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积攒热量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却无缘亲近暖暖的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无缘亲近也不气馁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把生命收紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓缩太阳的形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉默无言的土豆呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生在深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长在暗处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土豆　土豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憨憨的土豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地是你惟一的亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开了土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会断肠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当之无愧的大地之子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地的本色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土的芬香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风为谁歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻了身的土地涌着自由的波浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光打了个照面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匆匆　土豆们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又走进比土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更深的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天秋天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为秋天里流汗的双亲流泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上的包谷是爹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下的土豆是娘"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":14,"page_end":14}